Detailed Description

Class that holds a number of NParams.

Can parse a byte buffer with parameter data.

NParam& NParamBlock::addParam (  const NParam &  param  ) 
 

Add a NParam.

Is copied and reference is returned. To add a large parameter it is best to first call addParam then addByteArray on the returned param. This avoids copying the big buffer.
